ights to elucidate the nature of\n\\emph{holographic} BKT transitions, from the field theory side, a result which\nhas remained elusive to date. We derive the QCD phase diagram for $\\mu_B$ above\nthe baryon mass and find good agreement with results obtained by other methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 May 2018 16:03:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 May 2018 20:09:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2019 22:45:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-25"}
