olution, they fluctuate around tracks associated with\ntheir halo properties, i.e. galaxies above/below the main sequence at $z = 0.1$\ntend to have been above/below the main sequence for $\\gg1$ Gyr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 May 2018 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2019 09:16:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-16"}
